content.text: \(𝔾Ø = (𝕂, d, Φ, SØ)\) where: - \(𝕂\) – set of cognitive layers \((P_0, R, I, A, Ø)\) - \(d: 𝕂 × 𝕂 → ℝ⁺ ∪ \{∞\}\) – cognitive metric - \(Φ: 𝕂 → ℝ^n\) – embedding function of layers into geometric space - \(SØ\) – indefiniteness singularity: geometric center, infinite density point, and definitional nullity
